### 5.1 Object.create(prototype[,propertiesObject])
### 5.2 Obeject.getPrototypeOf()
### 5.3 Object.setPrototypeOf(obj,prototype)
### 5.4 Object.freeze()
### 5.5 Object.isFrozen()
### 5.6 Object.preventExtension()
### 5.7 Object.isExtensible()
